++ System Portal

The SP is similar to ApplicationPortalling except it is for TheSystem. The SP aims to present important ongoing [Configuration]:

    * [Servers] running
    * Discovered from [Indexing]
    * Virtual Private [Network]s

[Search] is also available from the SP. The following information is searchable from appropriate [Indexing]:
    * [Configuration]
    * [Files]
    * [History]
    * UserLists
    * SystemInformation
    * [Documentation]
    * [Tasks]

InterfacePanels for results are presented in ListStyle